Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.74,0:00:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Up until now, I've insisted\Non "using" One For All.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.37,0:00:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should've turned the switch\Non throughout from the beginning!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.91,0:00:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Imagining the heat that used\Nto only be in one place...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.54,0:00:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...spreading throughout my whole body!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.92,0:00:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna give it a try?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.88,0:00:25.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.14,0:00:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.23,0:02:02.23,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Izuku Midoriya - Quirk: One For All"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.31,0:02:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To keep One For All going\Nthroughout your whole body.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.27,0:02:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can move while maintaining that,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.78,0:02:08.99,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Pro Hero - Gran Torino - Quirk: Jet"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.57,0:02:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then you'll be completely different\Nfrom how you were at the sports festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.74,0:02:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, what will you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.91,0:02:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll start with three minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.75,0:02:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three... minutes...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.92,0:02:24.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try getting a hit on me in that time!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.80,0:02:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap, he dodged!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.64,0:02:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.81,0:02:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't even react to this,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.23,0:02:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then you won't be able to\Nsave those that could be saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.77,0:02:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone extolled as the Symbol of Peace
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.94,0:02:49.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,would be able to get over this wall in a jiffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.53,0:02:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One For A--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.95,0:02:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll take time to get it going\Nthrough my whole body again...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.20,0:02:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A single hit doesn't pack much punch,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.00,0:03:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but he's too fast to follow with my eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.79,0:03:06.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I just need a little time!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.46,0:03:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.63,0:03:09.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.09,0:03:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.68,0:03:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't be able to buy time like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.10,0:03:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.52,0:03:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were trying to get me to stop moving, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.10,0:03:23.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.19,0:03:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One For All...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.73,0:03:28.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Full Cowling!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.57,0:03:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Almost.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.07,0:03:33.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.24,0:03:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the same as last time, kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.00,0:03:47.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smash...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.67,0:03:50.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He can dodge this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.56,0:03:57.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.81,0:03:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.85,0:04:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard just to keep it going...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.06,0:04:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've still got a long way to go...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.98,0:04:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you were able to attack me when I was\Nunguarded through analysis and prediction.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.82,0:04:13.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think about a lot of stuff\Nnormally, don't you, kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.28,0:04:18.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just since yesterday you've already\Nchanged a lot with just one attempt...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.70,0:04:24.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You made me dodge seriously\Nfor the first time in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.71,0:04:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This kid might become a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.30,0:04:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, now you've gotta get used to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.09,0:04:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's keep right on going!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.21,0:04:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.18,0:04:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But before that,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.34,0:04:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,now that I think about it,\Nwe haven't had breakfast yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.72,0:04:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We... haven't!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.18,0:04:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So go heat up the {\i1}taiyaki{\i} again...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.56,0:04:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They fell!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.94,0:04:48.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'll go buy more!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.32,0:04:53.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've still got a long way to go,\Nbut I could see the light.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.53,0:04:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One For All: Full Cowling...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.20,0:04:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll definitely make it my own!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.16,0:05:03.16,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Midoriya and Shigaraki"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.16,0:05:04.66,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Mind, Skill, Body"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.71,0:05:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi-yah! Hi-yah! Hi-yah! Hi-yah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.71,0:05:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do it aimlessly.\NMake sure you focus on each action, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.55,0:05:16.55,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Pro Hero - Gunhead"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.47,0:05:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because what counts the most in\Nthe end is your basic physical strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.01,0:05:20.56,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Ochaco Uraraka - Quirk: Zero Gravity"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.43,0:05:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.64,0:05:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He acts cute, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.52,0:05:22.64,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Pro Hero - Fourth Kind"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.56,0:05:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's lukewarm!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.64,0:05:26.27,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Tetsutetsu Tetsutetsu - Quirk: Steel"\N"Eijiro Kirishima - Quirk: Hardening"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.10,0:05:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two can't even make a decent cup of tea?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.69,0:05:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Clients come to the office, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.57,0:05:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you gonna do if you\Ncan't even attend to them properly?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.03,0:05:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Mr. Fourth Kind!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.36,0:05:40.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, it's really satisfying to hit your Quirks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.62,0:05:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.66,0:05:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.83,0:05:49.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A hero must give the people\Nwho need rescuing peace of mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.29,0:05:54.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be capable, of course, but your\Nphysical appearance, speech, and actions
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.63,0:05:57.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,must be elegant if you're a hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.97,0:05:59.43,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Pro Hero - Best Jeanist"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.43,0:05:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.84,0:06:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.97,0:06:02.35,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Katsuki Bakugo - Quirk: Explosion"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.10,0:06:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.51,0:06:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, Best Jeanist!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.48,0:06:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I came to the wrong place...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.86,0:06:14.61,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Pro Hero - Uwabami"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.07,0:06:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After this photoshoot, she'll be a guest on\Na radio show and a magazine interview, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.57,0:06:22.91,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Itsuka Kendo - Quirk: Big Fist"\N"Momo Yaoyorozu - Quirk: Creation"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.70,0:06:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're basically just her entourage...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.62,0:06:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think this is a necessary\Npart of being a hero, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.08,0:06:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure there is something to learn here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.13,0:06:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.46,0:06:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.55,0:06:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She doesn't want to accept it...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.30,0:06:44.81,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Lounge"\N"In use"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.18,0:06:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to intrude so suddenly, All Might.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.22,0:06:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right, Tsukauchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.81,0:06:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, what did you find out?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.94,0:06:54.94,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Police Officer - Naomasa Tsukauchi"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.65,0:06:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Among those who attacked USJ, there was\Nthe villain Nomu that you drove back, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.45,0:07:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That strong guy, huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.16,0:07:04.66,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Pro Hero - All Might - Quirk: One For All"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.66,0:07:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We did some tests on Nomu's DNA.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.95,0:07:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,DNA tests?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.54,0:07:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.79,0:07:12.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not asking for your help in this\Ninvestigation, so I'd be leaking information,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.67,0:07:15.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I felt like I just had to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.71,0:07:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a clue to lead us to the mastermind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.55,0:07:22.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After investigating Nomu\Nat a specialized institution,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.72,0:07:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we realized that it wasn't that Nomu can't talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.51,0:07:27.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no reaction no matter what we do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.64,0:07:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is literally unable to think for himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.48,0:07:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And regarding his identity...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.06,0:07:36.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We found out that he was just a thug with\Na criminal record of assault and extortion.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.78,0:07:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you're saying that's\Na lead to the mastermind?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.70,0:07:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.61,0:07:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,According to the report, there's DNA\Nfrom at least four completely different people
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.04,0:07:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,intermingled inside this thug's body.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.08,0:07:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,DNA from at least four people intermingled...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.92,0:07:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he even human?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.59,0:08:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His whole body appears to have been tampered\Nwith using drugs and other methods.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.55,0:08:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To oversimplify a bit, he's been modified\Nso his body can hold multiple Quirks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.18,0:08:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The huge drop in his brain's processing power\Nprobably comes from the burden that causes,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.60,0:08:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but well, what we're more\Nconcerned about is his DNA...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.56,0:08:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and how he has multiple Quirks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.86,0:08:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if different DNA is introduced,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.90,0:08:22.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,unless there is some way\Nit can be completely integrated,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.45,0:08:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the bearer would not have multiple Quirks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.28,0:08:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must understand, since you have One For All.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.20,0:08:34.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's very likely that there is someone\Nwith a Quirk that can give others Quirks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.87,0:08:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.50,0:08:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looking at the circumstances,\Nit would be reasonable to assume such.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.51,0:08:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I thought I had to let you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.68,0:08:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Has that man... started to move again...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.56,0:08:58.40,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Karaoke"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.40,0:09:02.28,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Mahjong"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.86,0:09:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you want to add me to your numbers?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.78,0:09:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what you want to accomplish,\Nit is necessary to have conviction and desire.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.03,0:09:10.99,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Villain - Stain"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.28,0:09:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those without it and those\Nwho are weak will be weeded out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.70,0:09:12.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's only natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.91,0:09:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why it turns out like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.17,0:09:18.63,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Villain - Tomura Shigaraki - Quirk: Decay"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.71,0:09:19.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oww... That's too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.84,0:09:22.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurogiri, take this guy back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.34,0:09:26.34,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Villain - Kurogiri - Quirk: Warp Gate"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.51,0:09:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I can't move my body...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.76,0:09:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be the hero killer's Quirk...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.10,0:09:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This society overgrown with fake heroes,\Nwhere the word itself has lost its true meaning,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.73,0:09:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the criminals who\Nwave their power around idly
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.69,0:09:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,should all be purged.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.82,0:09:43.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait a sec...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.53,0:09:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not this palm...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.78,0:09:48.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.74,0:09:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure talk a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.87,0:09:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conviction?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.50,0:09:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have anything grand like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.62,0:09:58.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I had to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.37,0:10:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it'd be All Might.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.75,0:10:05.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like I really want\Nto completely crush this society,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.51,0:10:09.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,where trash like that gets worshipped.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.31,0:10:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My last injury was finally\Nabout to finish healing...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.48,0:10:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have a healer in our party, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.69,0:10:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you take responsibility for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.82,0:10:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's who you are...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.78,0:10:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.95,0:10:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems our goals oppose each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.53,0:10:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, we do agree on\None thing--to destroy the present.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.25,0:10:40.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop messing around. Go home. Die.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.63,0:10:43.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the kind of person you hate the most, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.17,0:10:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was testing your true motives.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.46,0:10:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People show their true colors\Nwhen they're on the verge of death.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.01,0:10:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's different,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.51,0:10:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but there is "desire"--a warped\Nsprout of conviction living inside you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.68,0:11:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How will you bud?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.06,0:11:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It might not be too late to wait until\Nafter I've seen that to dispose of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.19,0:11:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna dispose of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.03,0:11:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.49,0:11:14.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurogiri, I don't want someone\Nthis crazy as a party member.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.16,0:11:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomura Shigaraki, he will be\Na great asset if he joins us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.62,0:11:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The negotiations were successful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.17,0:11:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My business is done.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.79,0:11:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, return me to Hosu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.05,0:11:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are still things I must attend to there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.68,0:11:38.10,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Pro Hero - Manual"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.35,0:11:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, with the whole city on alert,\Nvillains can't come out, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.48,0:11:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.81,0:11:48.82,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Tenya Iida - Quirk: Engine"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.82,0:11:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hero Killer: Stain.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.36,0:11:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew immediately after\NI collected the information.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.32,0:11:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the seven places he has appeared so far,\Nhe always injured at least four heroes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.95,0:11:57.87,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Serial Slasher - Five Heroes Killed"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.87,0:12:03.17,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Still at Large"\N"People Question the Investigation"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.58,0:12:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if there is a purpose\Nbehind that, or if it's just a superstition,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.00,0:12:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but that's what always happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.17,0:12:06.88,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Another Nightmare"\N"Hero Attack in Hosu City"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.63,0:12:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In Hosu, Tensei's still\Nthe only one who was attacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.75,0:12:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenya... I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.47,0:12:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's very likely that he\Nwill appear in this city again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.81,0:12:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come! I will dispose of you with these hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.02,0:12:29.03,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Tenya Iida"\N"Quirk: Engine"\N"He can run very fast with the engines on his calves."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.02,0:12:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Affiliation: U.A. High School Hero Class 1-A"\N"Birthday: 8/22"\N"Height: 179 cm" "Blood Type: A" "Likes: Beef Stew"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.03,0:12:33.03,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Stain"\N"Quirk: Unknown"\N"Unknown"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.03,0:12:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Affiliation: Unknown"\N"Birthday: Unknown"\N"Height: Unknown" "Blood Type: Unknown" "Likes: Unknown"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.24,0:12:35.53,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Internships - Day 3"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.53,0:12:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keeping the 5%
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.95,0:12:41.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and attacking.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.21,0:12:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's stop now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.42,0:12:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you fight against my tactics more\Nthan this, you might fall into weird habits.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.80,0:12:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't even think about tactics right now.\NI'm still not used to this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.47,0:12:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please let me fight more!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.72,0:12:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.43,0:13:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Change into your costume.\NLet's move on to Phase 2!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.10,0:13:05.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.35,0:13:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.48,0:13:10.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go fight some villains!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.07,0:13:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? All of a sudden?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.53,0:13:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you only fight against me,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.20,0:13:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then you'll have trouble when you\Ncome across a completely different type!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.53,0:13:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The next phase is to let you\Nexperience different types and situations!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.08,0:13:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the first place, this is an internship.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.00,0:13:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course you'll be fighting villains.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.37,0:13:28.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What you are saying is quite right,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.96,0:13:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I need more time to prepare myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.63,0:13:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've already experienced\Ncombat against villains, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.05,0:13:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, we're not gonna\Ntouch anything that big.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.72,0:13:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll go on a little excursion.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.35,0:13:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of the decreasing population\Nin this area, the crime rate is also low.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.06,0:13:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The reason there are a lot of hero agencies\Nin urban areas is that there is a lot of crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.61,0:13:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the higher the population density,\Nthe more trouble you'll find.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.45,0:13:59.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Around Shibuya, you'll find lots of\Nsmall fights that break out on a daily basis.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.49,0:14:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By Shibuya, you mean the one in Tokyo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.41,0:14:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think I'd be wearing my\Nhero costume in such a fashionable town!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.37,0:14:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wouldn't get to wear it\Nif you weren't with a hero, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.08,0:14:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be happy that you'll get to display\Nit on such a wonderful stage!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.84,0:14:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.05,0:14:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we'll take the bullet train\Nfrom Kofu heading toward Shinjuku?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.97,0:14:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.34,0:14:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll pass Hosu City...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.51,0:14:22.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how Iida's doing...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.81,0:14:26.31,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Same Time - Hosu City"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.47,0:14:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try to get in touch with him later.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.60,0:14:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be patrolling Kyoto today, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.77,0:14:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry it's so monotonous.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.90,0:14:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine. It is actually better this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.03,0:14:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.57,0:14:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is kind of hard to ask,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.70,0:14:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you're chasing after\Nthe hero killer, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.12,0:14:43.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.37,0:14:46.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't think of any other reason\Nwhy you'd come to my agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.75,0:14:50.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but I'm really glad you came!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.25,0:14:55.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just, you shouldn't\Nact on a personal grudge.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.05,0:14:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We heroes do not have\Nthe authority to arrest or punish.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.34,0:15:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The use of Quirks has been\Nallowed through their regulation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.93,0:15:07.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is why, no matter what the reason,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.35,0:15:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,heroes must not use their Quirks for themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.15,0:15:14.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If anyone used their Quirk\Nfor their own selfish desires,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.02,0:15:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it would be a very serious crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.90,0:15:22.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's not that I'm saying\Nthe hero killer isn't guilty.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.28,0:15:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just because you seem so earnest,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.95,0:15:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,like you'd focus on one thing\Nand ignore everything else,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.12,0:15:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I was worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.20,0:15:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for the warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.29,0:15:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's fine as long as you understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.04,0:15:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, shall we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.79,0:15:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.00,0:15:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But then... what am I supposed\Nto do... about these feelings?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.02,0:15:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hosu City looks nicer than I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.73,0:15:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what are you gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.23,0:16:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will reform this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.28,0:16:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to do so, I require more victims.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.82,0:16:07.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this what you meant the other day\Nwhen you said you had business to take care of?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.91,0:16:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see you're someone who understands.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.62,0:16:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what're you trying to say about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.58,0:16:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Hero" is a title given only to those\Nwho have accomplished great deeds!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.76,0:16:21.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are too many...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.55,0:16:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too many who act like heroes\Nbut are really money-worshippers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.72,0:16:28.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until this world realizes its mistake,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.64,0:16:31.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will continue to appear.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.56,0:16:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He talks all high and mighty like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.19,0:16:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but basically he's trying to start\Na grassroots movement, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.98,0:16:41.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's so noble I could cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.19,0:16:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't make fun of him too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.70,0:16:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The reality is that in all the cities\Nwhere Stain has appeared,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.91,0:16:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the crime rate has fallen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.83,0:16:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some critics attribute this\Nto a rise in heroes' consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.04,0:16:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and shoot him down, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.25,0:16:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.63,0:17:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heroes are working hard to\Nbring down the cost of food, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.76,0:17:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So the "hero killer" is also a "hero breeder"!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.26,0:17:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too roundabout.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.22,0:17:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We just can't agree at a basic level.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.73,0:17:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he annoys me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.60,0:17:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurogiri, bring out the Nomus.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.52,0:17:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think you can get away with stabbing me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.36,0:17:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I want to kill you, I just will. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.83,0:17:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be a wild contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.20,0:17:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll crush your honor and your pride, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.67,0:17:42.13,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Near Hosu City"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.55,0:17:46.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, this train won't arrive\Nuntil night. Is that okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.97,0:17:48.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why it's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.34,0:17:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There'll be more skirmishes then,\Nso it'll be more fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.39,0:17:55.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't sound fun, but I guess I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.81,0:18:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Using his smartphone with\Nsomeone next to him! Kids these days!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.31,0:18:02.28,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"See you tomorrow! (read)"\N"Yeah! See you tomorrow, then! (read)"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.28,0:18:04.40,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Today"\N"I'll be passing near Hosu!! How are\Nthings going with you, Iida? (read)"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.40,0:18:07.41,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"(read)"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.94,0:18:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He read the message but didn't reply...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.95,0:18:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Iida usually responds within\Nthree minutes of reading the message...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.49,0:18:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're almost at Hosu Station, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.50,0:18:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you ever feel hopeless,\Nmake sure you let us know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.83,0:18:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're friends, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.88,0:18:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.30,0:18:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.84,0:18:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That building just exploded!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.51,0:18:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where? Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.80,0:18:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What's going on?\N--You're right! There's smoke!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.97,0:18:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Could it be a fire?\N--You're right! There's smoke!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.18,0:18:35.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Passengers, please hold onto your seats.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.23,0:18:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.03,0:18:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A hero?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.45,0:18:51.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nomu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.32,0:18:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kid, sit down!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.95,0:18:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grand Torino?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.83,0:19:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grand Torino!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.55,0:19:10.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What is it...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.18,0:19:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.81,0:19:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is good. Let's make this flashy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.52,0:19:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say? A villain appeared?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.61,0:19:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. We'll head over right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.19,0:19:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenya!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.86,0:19:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna run!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.57,0:19:32.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.53,0:19:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, this is different.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.87,0:19:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That guy wouldn't be so flashy...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.59,0:19:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So noisy...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.72,0:19:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The idiots have come out, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.84,0:19:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll dispose of them later.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.22,0:19:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.52,0:20:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will do what I should be doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.52,0:20:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My body... won't move...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.90,0:20:06.48,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Pro Hero - Native"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.81,0:20:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.90,0:20:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Die...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.40,0:20:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you call yourself a hero,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.86,0:20:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you should choose your last words carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.33,0:20:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A child wearing a suit...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.71,0:20:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.55,0:20:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go away. This is not a place for children.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.51,0:20:41.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A scarf as red as blood,\Ncarrying blades all over your body...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.14,0:20:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be the Hero Killer: Stain!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.10,0:20:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.98,0:20:48.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have been chasing you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.48,0:20:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did not think I would find you so soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.36,0:20:54.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.07,0:20:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your eyes... Are you here for vengeance?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.16,0:20:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful of what you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.45,0:21:04.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Depending on the situation,\Neven children may become my targets.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.12,0:21:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying that I am... not even a target?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.34,0:21:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then listen, criminal!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.26,0:21:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the younger brother of a hero you attacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.60,0:21:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The younger brother of\Na most excellent older brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.89,0:21:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have come to stop you in his place!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.57,0:21:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you take this name for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.69,0:21:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember my name for as long as you live!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.91,0:21:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ingenium. It is the name of\Nthe hero who will defeat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.54,0:21:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.58,0:21:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Die.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.05,0:23:22.05,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Preview"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.63,0:23:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's the preview!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.89,0:23:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hosu City is under attack by villains, where...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.60,0:23:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have found you, Hero Killer: Stain!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.89,0:23:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the younger brother of a hero you attacked!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.56,0:23:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is the reason\Nwhy Iida chose this internship...
